  <div class="page" id="about">
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="about-hero-bg"></div>
      <div class="about-hero-content">
        <p class="section-label">About</p>
        <h1 class="about-title">Where technique<br>meets <em>instinct.</em></h1>
      </div>
    </section>
    <div class="about-body">
      <div class="about-copy">
        <p><strong>Amanda Jean Prestipino</strong> is a DMV-based luxury makeup artist with 8 years of professional experience and formal training from a nationally accredited makeup school in Los Angeles.</p>
        <p>Her foundation is technical — rooted in skin theory, face structure, color balance, longevity, and lighting. Not just trends. She brings the precision of a trained professional and the intuition of an artist who has spent thousands of hours in the chair.</p>
        <p>Amanda specializes in bridal and event makeup that looks timeless on camera and in person. Her approach is intentional, detail-driven, and deeply personal. She reads faces the way a sculptor reads form — finding what enhances rather than what changes.</p>
        <p>Every client sits down as themselves and leaves as the <strong>best version of themselves.</strong> Not someone else's vision. Not whatever is trending on Instagram. Yours.</p>
        <p>She serves brides and clients throughout the DMV and is available for destination weddings. For production and editorial work, reach out through the contact page.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-credentials">
        <div class="credential-item"><div class="credential-label">Experience</div><div class="credential-value">8 Years Professional</div></div>
        <div class="credential-item"><div class="credential-label">Training</div><div class="credential-value">Nationally Accredited School<br>Los Angeles, CA</div></div>
        <div class="credential-item"><div class="credential-label">Specialization</div><div class="credential-value">Bridal · Event · Editorial</div></div>
        <div class="credential-item"><div class="credential-label">Location</div><div class="credential-value">DMV Based<br>Available Nationwide</div></div>
        <div class="credential-item"><div class="credential-label">Philosophy</div><div class="credential-value">Timeless over trendy.<br>Technical over surface.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <section class="philosophy-section">
      <p class="philosophy-quote">"I'm not here to put a face on you. I'm here to show you what was always there."</p>
      <p class="philosophy-attr">— Amanda Jean Prestipino</p>
    </section>
